<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Cannabis Board </title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="font-awesome.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
      <h1 id="postit">the circle</h1>
    

    <ul class="messages">
      <% for(var i=0; i<messages.length; i++) {%>
        <% let color = messages[i].priority === 'high' ? 'green' : 'black' %>
        <li class="message">
          <span id="<%= color %>"><%=messages[i].msg%></span><br><br>
          <span><%=messages[i].thumbUp%></span>
          <span id="<%=messages[i]._id%>"></span>
          <span ><i class="fa fa-leaf" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
          <span><i class="fa fa-trash" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><br>
        </li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>


  <section class="form">
    <form action="/messages" method="POST">
      <textarea type="text" placeholder="story time (green text) / what'd you try(black text)?" name="msg"></textarea> <br><br>
      <span> Check if you're telling a story:</span>
      <input type="radio" id="mark" name="priority"><br>
      <button type="submit">Create Post</button>
    </form>

    <h4>leaf icon = enjoyed this in the past</h4>
    <h4>trash icon = delete post</h4>

      <p>Use this  board to post about:</p>
      <p>Cannabis Stains/Concentrates</p>
      <p>New ways you've learned to consume THC (Edibles: Candies, Drinks, Sauces etc. )</p>
      <p>Cannabinoids -- fun fact</p>
      <p>Topicals - lotions, oils etc. / Tinctures</p>
      <p>Tell a high story lol</p>
  </section>

  <script src="/public/main.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
